<span id="freeTextContainer9990862998612422197">This is NOT really book 3, it&apos;s the end of book 2 &amp; a fine way to wrap it up, too. There aren&apos;t any surprises, but it is a lot of fun.</span>
  <span id="freeText9990862998612422197" style="display:none">This is NOT really book 3, it's the end of book 2 &amp; a fine way to wrap it up, too. There aren't any surprises, but it is a lot of fun.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9990862998612422197" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


