<span id="freeTextContainer947219408787364560">Another fast paced adventure on Mars! There were a few times where John&apos;s escapes were a little too easy, just one lucky dodge, a lucky catch, ect, and few places where I felt he should have realized things but overall, this was a pretty good story. It&apos;s a good way to spend a few hours, at any rate!</span>
  <span id="freeText947219408787364560" style="display:none">Another fast paced adventure on Mars! There were a few times where John's escapes were a little too easy, just one lucky dodge, a lucky catch, ect, and few places where I felt he should have realized things but overall, this was a pretty good story. It's a good way to spend a few hours, at any rate!</span>
